      <title>葛兰素史克上调 2024 年利润预期，但表示下半年销售额增长将放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/gsk-raises-full-year-profit-forecast-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于疫苗和特种药物的强劲需求，葛兰素史克周三上调了全年利润预期，尽管该公司指出下半年销售增长将放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/gsk-raises-full-year-profit-forecast-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 06:08:19 GMT</pubDate>
